# Gender Detection Using Machine Learning

## Description
This project predicts gender based on a persons name.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Flask
- HTML
- CSS

## Files
- app.py
- train_model.py
- gender_dataset.csv
- model.pkl
- vectorizer.pkl

## How to Run

Install packages:

pip install pandas numpy scikit-learn flask

Train model:

python train_model.py

Run project:

python app.py

Open browser:

http://127.0.0.1:5000

## Output
Predicts Male or Female from entered name.